    },
    {
      "role": "body",
      "left_in": 1.4,
      "top_in": 3.05,
      "width_in": 10.83,
      "height_in": 0.65,
      "text": "Building in stealth.  Months of code. Zero customer conversations. The market is silent until you launch \u2014 by then it is too late.",
      "font_size_pt": 19.0,
      "font_bold": true,
      "font_italic": false,
      "font_name": "SF Pro Display",
      "color": "090B11",
      "fill": null,
      "alignment": "left",
      "z": 4
    },
    {
      "role": "body",
      "left_in": 1.4,
      "top_in": 3.88,
      "width_in": 10.83,
      "height_in": 0.65,
      "text": "Adding features instead of finding problems.  Every new feature is a hypothesis. Test problems, not features.",
      "font_size_pt": 19.0,
      "font_bold": true,
      "font_italic": false,
      "font_name": "SF Pro Display",
      "color": "090B11",
      "fill": null,
      "alignment": "left",
      "z": 6
    },
    {
      "role": "body",
      "left_in": 1.4,
      "top_in": 4.71,
      "width_in": 10.83,
      "height_in": 0.65,
      "text": "Optimizing the wrong thing.  Speed of code matters less than speed of learning. Ship ugly. Learn fast.",
      "font_size_pt": 19.0,
      "font_bold": true,
      "font_italic": false,
      "font_name": "SF Pro Display",
      "color": "090B11",
      "fill": null,
      "alignment": "left",
      "z": 8
    },
    {
      "role": "body",
      "left_in": 1.4,
      "top_in": 5.54,
      "width_in": 10.83,
      "height_in": 0.65,
      "text": "Avoiding sales.  Sales is a skill, not a personality. If you do not sell, your product does not get used.",
      "font_size_pt": 19.0,
      "font_bold": true,
      "font_italic": false,
      "font_name": "SF Pro Display",
      "color": "090B11",
      "fill": null,
      "alignment": "left",
      "z": 10
